    <ul>
      <li>The quizzes and content provided are for educational and entertainment purposes only.</li>
      <li>BioBrain does not guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or reliability of any content.</li>
      <li>Users are responsible for their own actions and decisions based on quiz results.</li>
      <li>Participation in quizzes is voluntary, and any outcomes are non-binding.</li>
      <li>BioBrain is not liable for any losses, damages, or misunderstandings resulting from using this platform.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Please use the platform responsibly and verify information from trusted sources when needed.</p>

    <a href="/" class="btn-home">Back to Home</a>
  </div>

  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <%- include('../../partials/desktop/footer') %>
</body>
</html>